  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\n\r\nOn some Android devices, when the height of the bottom sheet is max, the top margin differs from the designs. \r\nOriginally was discovered while testing https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/18003\r\n\r\nExpected height:\r\n<img width=\"805\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-12-04 at 14 03 45\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/67952253/780674b2-e98c-4a93-b429-4a4082af6131\">\r\n\r\n\r\nBottom sheet max-height on devices with a punch-hole selfie camera (Pixel 7a in this case):\r\n\r\n<img width=\"284\" alt=\"Screenshot 2023-12-04 at 14 00 14\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/67952253/ef370f2f-9cbf-4825-9d17-40d6c04bf96e\">\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n@smohamedjavid's [comment](https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/18003#issuecomment-1838540911):\r\n\r\n> It works as expected on iOS devices and for Android devices that don't have a punch-hole selfie camera.\r\n> The sheet's max height behaves differently on devices with a punch-hole selfie camera than the devices without it.\r\n> Adjusting the bottom sheet max-height calculation should not affect existing sheets in the app.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1. Create multiple wallet accounts in the new wallet\r\n2. Tap on the Account Avatar (Switcher) in the top right corner to open the account options + switcher sheet\r\n\r\nor \r\n\r\n1. Open a chat\r\n2. Send a long message/message with an image and a multi-line description \r\n3. Send the message\r\n4. Long press on the message to open options and the message preview\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly 4/12\r\n- Operating System: Android\r\n\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please, add logs/notes if necessary)\r\n\r\n",
